          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-d5365efd3c5abc2f",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Here\u2019s how to earn up to $600\nSTEP 1\nOpen your first CIBC Smart Account, then within 2 months, set up at least one recurring direct deposit of $500 or more per month from your employer, government or pension. Learn about direct deposits. Opens a dialog.\nSTEP 2\nNow, you\u2019re ready to earn $500 with your Smart Account plus $100 with any eligible credit card by completing these qualifying actions.\nEarn\n$500\nwith a CIBC Smart Account. Within 60 days of opening your Smart Account, complete one of the following actions within the same calendar month:\n2 recurring pre-authorized debits Learn about pre-authorized debits. Opens a dialog.\n2 online bill payments of $50 or more each Opens a new window.\n5 eligible Visa* Debit purchases Learn more about Visa debit purchases. Opens a dialog.\n+\nEarn\n$100\nwhen you apply and get approved for any eligible credit card within one month of opening your CIBC",
