          "evidence_text_excerpt": "ownload the award-winning CIBC Mobile Banking App\nUse your debit or credit card to register for CIBC Banking\nNow you're ready to bank on the go, anytime, anywhere.\nTo find a CIBC Banking Centre or ATM, use our branch and ATM locator Opens a new window. . Enter your address or postal code. You\u2019ll find the following banking centre details: telephone and fax numbers, branch transit number, accessibility options and a list of available services and hours of operation .\nWith CIBC Smart Arrival, permanent residents, foreign workers and international students from eligible countries can apply for a temporary bank account before arriving in Canada \u24d8 .\nLearn more about CIBC Smart Arrival",
